commit 9602a9f11dd5ac928a7275ceb1a58d5328b9d49e
Author: Alan Coopersmith <alan.coopersmith@oracle.com>
Date:   Thu Feb 1 18:16:59 2024 -0800

    greeter: Constify value argument to SetValue()
    
