    Mark LogPanic as noreturn per gcc's suggestion
    
    error.c: In function ‘LogPanic’:
    error.c:93:1: warning: function might be candidate for attribute ‘noreturn’
     [-Wsuggest-attribute=noreturn]
     LogPanic (const char * fmt, ...)
